{
  "query": "document summary",
  "collection_name": "example",
  "limit": 3
}


### ============================================================================
### Web Search Endpoints - Quick Examples
### ============================================================================

### General web search
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "latest technology trends",
  "category": "general",
  "language": "en",
  "time_range": "week",
  "page": 1,
  "per_page": 10
}

### Web search with bang syntax (!gh = GitHub, !so = Stack Overflow, etc.)
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "python framework",
  "bang": "!gh",
  "language": "en",
  "time_range": "month",
  "page": 1,
  "per_page": 10
}

### Specialized category search
POST http://localhost:8000/web-search/specialized
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "docker kubernetes",
  "category": "it",
  "language": "en",
  "time_range": "year",
  "page": 1,
  "per_page": 10
}

### Get available bang shortcuts
GET http://localhost:8000/web-search/bangs

### Get available categories
GET http://localhost:8000/web-search/categories

### Get bang syntax help and examples
GET http://localhost:8000/web-search/bangs/syntax


