### ============================================================================
### Test Execution
### ============================================================================
### 
### Services:
### - Server: make r (http://localhost:8000)
### - SearXNG: make up (http://localhost:8888)
### 
### Run comprehensive web search tests:
### - Open: tests/http/web_search.http
### - Use REST Client extension to execute requests
### 
### Expected responses:
### - Success: 200 OK with JSON results
### - Bang not found: 400 Bad Request
### - Timeout: 504 Gateway Timeout
### - Service unavailable: 503 Service Unavailable
### 
### Prerequisites:
### - python -m spacy download en_core_web_sm
### - Docker services running (Qdrant, SearXNG)
### 
